creator: Digistorm Education
descriptionHtml:
Access the key features of Rouse Hill Anglican College from the palm of your hand with the Rouse Hill Anglican College app, developed in partnership with Digistorm and Edumate. Receive instant and important information from your school community, receive real-time alerts and experience seamless collaboration between your users.

Key features of the Rouse Hill Anglican College app:

Newsfeed: An aggregated view of the latest Broadcasts and Space Posts from the last 30 days.

Calendar: The Calendar provides carers a personalised view of what's coming up for the day or in the future.

To-Do: Access your Appointments and Event request. You will also be able to action these items by Accepting or Declining the item all from within the app.

Tasks: This module allows careers to know and be reminded when their tasks are due.

Timetable: The timetable feature pulls information dynamically from Edumate so that careers can view their child's class schedule.

Events: This module will provide you with a list of events that have been approved/accepted by the carer.

Absence: Access all unacknowledged and unverified absences with your app, as well as absentee history. Carers can also acknowledge and verify each absence directly from the app.

Settings allows you to manage the frequency and type of notifications that you receive from Rouse Hill Anglican College.
Developed by Digistorm - Software for Smarter Schools.
